channel.title: Comments on: K’s Top Albums of 2009

item.title: By: fak3r
item.dc:creator: fak3r
item.description:
While our lists don't totally overlap, I'm seeing some things I probably need to hear, and have caught a lot of bands I'm really into in your other posts. Plus I am in complete agreement with your comment here about the Phoenix effort; what a fun one! My list of my 2009 favs here: http://fak3r.com/2010/02/05/best-music-of-2009/
...thanks.
item.content:encoded:
